Manage and develop a Visual Merchandizing for our brandsResponsible for the consistent brand alignment of the Visual Merchandizing principles and standards throughout our storesProvide Visual Merchandizing briefs for the appropriate retail spaceResponsible for window display and visual display for our storesCoordinate and manage VM with staff in store and store operational sightEffectively execute merchandizing guidelines and provide feedback which identifies creative and visual solutionsCorrespondence and reporting regularly with principlesBudgeting and management for store visual requirement Requirements: Diploma or Degree holder in Visual Merchandizing/Fashion Design/Fashion Marketing or related disciplineMinimum 2 years of professional hands-on technical experience in the area of visual merchandizing in Retail especially in Ladies Fashion ApparelPossess excellent fashion sense and able to identify future market trendsCreative and possesses an eye for detailsA great work ethic with the ability to work under pressure and tight deadlinesExcellent communication and coaching skillsEffective research, writing and presentation skillsDemonstrated experience with budgetTravelling to other cities might be required "Only short-listed candidates will be invited via e-mail/phone for Test and Interview "
